WEBVTT

00:04:27.165 --> 00:04:30.415
Richard Faynmanning magnitlar haqidagi 
suhbatidan boshlaymiz,

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:33.155
va katta yo'l bosib o'tilgach bu jarayonni
Jastin Biber va

00:04:33.179 --> 00:04:35.059
onasini intervyusi bilan yakunlaymiz.

00:04:35.083 --> 00:04:37.271
(Kulgu)

00:04:37.295 --> 00:04:39.058
Bu juda katta vaqt oladi.

00:04:39.082 --> 00:04:42.584
Shuning uchun ishlashga vaqt ajratish 
bizda deyarli o'xshamaydi.

00:04:42.608 --> 00:04:43.771
Meni kechir...

00:04:43.795 --> 00:04:44.960
(Xo'rsinadi)

00:04:46.325 --> 00:04:49.694
Xo'sh, aslida nima yuz beradi?

00:04:51.481 --> 00:04:54.172
Maymuncha - rulni boshqarish uchun

00:04:54.196 --> 00:04:55.450
yaxshi kandidat emas.

00:04:55.474 --> 00:04:57.419
U hozirgi vaqt bilan yashaydi.

00:04:57.443 --> 00:05:00.271
U o'tmishni eslamaydi va kelajakni 
bilmaydi.